---
description: Add a REST endpoint to an existing controller + register the route (modify-aware generator).
allowed-tools: Bash(gofasta g*)
argument-hint: <Resource> <METHOD> <path>  (e.g. Order POST /orders/{id}/archive)
---

Run `gofasta g endpoint $ARGUMENTS --dry-run --json` first to preview
the planned edits. Surface the controller/service/route changes,
then re-run without `--dry-run` to apply if approved. Run
`gofasta swagger` after to refresh OpenAPI docs.
